metadata.name: She bit the forbidden and became mother nature #1
metadata.description:
The sweet fruit spoke to me...
will it rejuvenate me....hopefully..
even the clouds conversation falls on
deaf ears..until it rains..thunder..and lighting falls..
I noticed myself despite my flaws..im a blessing to 
humanity..still trying to preserve my sanity..because I was created by a higher power..that has plans for me..to follow his words..desperate to find out if its vanity... 

More beautiful Ai art from Cannon Jones973..along with on the spot poetry written by Cannon Jones973..there will be other versions of this minted..enjoy each version and my journey of a Ai artist...I still do my tradition art along with abstract...these prompts that I create speaks to me and I usually make them on the spot..
